    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>本应用为游戏《灵缘 ～化谜解咒，缘影交织～》的试用版。</strong><br>内容包含从剧情开端开始的3段故事与2个可玩关卡，总游戏体验时长约为30分钟-1个小时。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304480/extras/e2ba25519854d4e614d59b696a89659f.poster.avif?t=1768289174\" width=616 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304480/extras/e2ba25519854d4e614d59b696a89659f.webm?t=1768289174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304480/extras/e2ba25519854d4e614d59b696a89659f.mp4?t=1768289174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304480/extras/86396e843aeca21ef8c6241f581775f3.poster.avif?t=1768289174\" width=616 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304480/extras/86396e843aeca21ef8c6241f581775f3.webm?t=1768289174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304480/extras/86396e843aeca21ef8c6241f581775f3.mp4?t=1768289174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304480/extras/3128d58822719ea1cea1528ac27df9c4.poster.avif?t=1768289174\" width=616 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304480/extras/3128d58822719ea1cea1528ac27df9c4.webm?t=1768289174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304480/extras/3128d58822719ea1cea1528ac27df9c4.mp4?t=1768289174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304480/extras/81b294607ddf9c122d51b3422279bf35.poster.avif?t=1768289174\" width=616 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304480/extras/81b294607ddf9c122d51b3422279bf35.webm?t=1768289174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏内容</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏的玩法核心为「文字解谜视觉小说」。<br>您需要在受诅咒的环境中寻找被隐藏的「灵符」字卡，<br>通过组合字卡，逐步揭示关键事件以破除诅咒，<br>之后您将能查看由「缘影」呈现的回忆片段。<br>透过您的选择，扭转命运，帮助她们抵达「彼岸」吧！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的文字解谜游戏结合小游戏元素，让每一步充满惊喜！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有猫耳、狐耳、兔耳的角色们纷纷登场，耳朵还会动起来呢！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >温柔体贴的傻姐姐、内心坚强的懦弱少女、自称神明的雌小鬼、外貌永恒的贤慧幼妻，你准备好与她们相遇了吗？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走进神秘的神社巫女世界，沉浸于浓厚的和风怪谈故事中，体验古老仪式与神秘力量的奇妙魅力... </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小建议</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏较适合可接受用阅读文字来体验游戏的玩家。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏解谜要素会需要透过文字去想像环境空间，并逐步观察变化来找到解谜线索，整体来说会需要些想像力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若对于以上两点的体验有较大挫折感，可于解谜时透过选单来查看「提示」，里面能找到解谜的关键步骤，游玩体验上能大幅减轻难度。</p></li></ul>",
